# RDX Revamp Governance

Marketing revamp is shipped. Work follows living docs in `docs/` (not archived phase plans).

## Before coding

1. Read `docs/PRODUCTS.md` — which product (marketing / lead desk / OS)
2. Read `docs/README.md` — confirm active track (maintenance / launch / OS / lead desk)
3. Open the relevant living doc (Launch Runbook, Ops, Lead Desk, OS Spec, or Standards)
4. State track + files to touch + files to avoid at session start

## Hard stops

- No mass deletes of legacy routes/API without founder OK
- No invented metrics or fake testimonials (see Content Copy Bank)
- No new npm packages without founder OK

## New code goes here

- `src/components/rdx/`
- `src/content/rdx/`
- `src/styles/rdx/tokens.css`
- OS: `src/app/(os)/os/`, `src/components/os/`

## End of session

Run `npm run build` and `npm run lint`. Update `docs/README.md` status if the track advanced.

Skills: `.agents/skills/rdx-revamp/` + `.agents/skills/hallmark/` for design.
Product map: `docs/PRODUCTS.md`.
